  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support for church-led peace building in South Sudan pilot</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This pilot project will focus on support for two local Inter Church Committees (ICCs) and their associated Regional Office to assess and build their capacity to implement the pillars of the APP. This six month pilot phase of the project will build the foundation for a two-year programme of support for the APP, including: best practice in capacity assessment and support for ICCs in developing training modules around pillar methodologies.</narrative>
  </description>
